Token.Abstract: The AnylineBarcodeModuleView class declares the programmatic interface for an object that manages easy access to Anylines barcode scanning mode. All its capabilities are bundled into this AnylineAbstractModuleView subclass. Management of the scanning process happens within the view object. It is configurable via interface builder.

Sets the type of code to recognize. Valid values are: kCodeTypeAztec, kCodeTypeCodabar, kCodeTypeCode39, kCodeTypeCode93, kCodeTypeCode128, kCodeTypeDataMatrix, kCodeTypeEAN8, kCodeTypeEAN13, kCodeTypeITF, kCodeTypePDF417, kCodeTypeQR, kCodeTypeRSS14, kCodeTypeRSSExpanded, kCodeTypeUPCA, kCodeTypeUPCE, kCodeTypeUPCEANExtension. Default are all of the above. (Deprecated: since 3.4)
